\varphi:S\to\Bbb N^3:\langle x,y,z\rangle\mapsto\begin{cases} \langle x+2z,z,y-x-z\rangle,&\text{if }x<y-z\\ \langle 2y-x,y,x-y+z\rangle,&\text{if }y-z<x<2y\\ \langle x-2y,x-y+z,y\rangle,&\text{if }x>2y\;; \end{cases}\tag{1}
